<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV23">
<l>puṉamō puṉattaya lēvaḻi pōku maruviṉaiyēṉ</l>
<l>maṉamō makaḷirnuṅ kāvalcol līrpuṇṭa rīkattaṅkēḻ</l>
<l>vaṉamō raṉaiyakaṇ ṇāṉkaṇṇaṉ vāṉā ṭamarunteyvat</l>
<l>tiṉamō raṉaiyīrka ḷāyivai yōnum miyalvukaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it the field or the mind of me with difficult karma who goes the way near</l>
<l>the field, girls, that is under your guard? Speak! Since you are like a group</l>
<l>of deities that live in the heavenly land of Kaṇṇaṉ, him with eyes</l>
<l>that are like a forest of lotus lustre, these, are they your qualities?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
